sentences: Craft is a Swedish black metal band, originally formed under the name "Nocta" in 1994.
As Nocta they recorded an unreleased demo in 1997 and subsequently changed their name to "Craft".

After drummer Daniel Halén decided to quit the band in 2005, the remaining members briefly considered putting the band on indefinite hold, but decided to continue and address his replacement in the future.
